%section#main-slider.no-margin
  .carousel.slide{"data-ride" => "carousel"}
    .carousel-inner
      .item.active
        .container
          .row
            .col-sm-12
              .carousel-content.center.centered
                %h2.boxed.animation.animated-item-1.fade-down WE HAVE A LARGE DATABASE OF ASTRONAUTS
                %p.boxed.animation.animated-item-2.fade-up You can also expand this database. Just register now!
                %br/
                %a.btn.btn-md.animation.bounce-in{:href => "#services"} Learn More
#content-wrapper
  %section#services.white
    .container
      .gap
      .row
        .col-md-12
          .center.gap.fade-down.section-heading
            %h2.main-title What can you do here?
            %hr/
            %p We maintain and, with your help, constantly expand the database of astronauts. After registration, you can do the following actions.

      .row
        .col-md-4.col-sm-6
          .service-block
            .pull-left.bounce-in
              %i.fa.fa-list.fa.fa-md
            .media-body.fade-up
              %h3.media-heading List of astronauts
              %p You can see list of all astronauts. There is a some filter by gender.
        .col-md-4.col-sm-6
          .service-block
            .pull-left.bounce-in
              %i.fa.fa-eye.fa.fa-md
            .media-body.fade-up
              %h3.media-heading Show
              %p You can see a specific astronaut page with info about astronaut such us a name, surname, some description, gender, age and the number of space visits.
        .col-md-4.col-sm-6
          .service-block
            .pull-left.bounce-in
              %i.fa.fa-plus.fa.fa-md
            .media-body.fade-up
              %h3.media-heading Create new
              %p You can create new astronauts. You can also export data from XML file!
              %a{:href => "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/XML", :target => "_blank"} More about XML

      .row
        .col-md-4.col-sm-6
          .service-block
            .pull-left.bounce-in
              %i.fa.fa-pencil.fa.fa-md
            .media-body.fade-up
              %h3.media-heading Edit
              %p You can update some info about specific astronaut. Please use this feature with reason.
        .col-md-4.col-sm-6
          .service-block
            .pull-left.bounce-in
              %i.fa.fa-trash.fa.fa-md
            .media-body.fade-up
              %h3.media-heading destroy
              %p You can destroy some astronaut from database.
      .gap
  %section#stats.divider-section
    .gap
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-3.col-xs-6
          .center.bounce-in
            %span.stat-icon
              %i.fas.fa-mars
            %h1
              %span.counter= Astronaut.all.mens.count
            %h3 Mens
        .col-md-3.col-xs-6
          .center.bounce-in
            %span.stat-icon
              %i.fas.fa-venus
            %h1
              %span.counter= Astronaut.all.womens.count
            %h3 Womens
        .col-md-3.col-xs-6
          .center.bounce-in
            %span.stat-icon
              %i.fas.fa-arrow-down
            %h1
              %span.counter= Astronaut.all.age_under_40.count
            %h3 Age under 40
        .col-md-3.col-xs-6
          .center.bounce-in
            %span.stat-icon
              %i.fas.fa-arrow-up
            %h1
              %span.counter= Astronaut.all.age_over_40.count
            %h3 Age over 40
    .gap

  %section#contact.white
    .container
      .gap
      .center.gap.fade-down.section-heading
        %h2.main-title Get In Touch
        %hr/
        %p Of an or game gate west face shed. ï»¿no great but music too old found arose.
      .gap
      .row
        .col-md-4.fade-up
          %h3 Contact Information
          %p
            %span.icon.icon-home>
            Time Square, New York
            %br/
            = succeed "+36" do
              %span.icon.icon-phone
            %br/
            = succeed "+36" do
              %span.icon.icon-mobile
            %br/
            %span.icon.icon-envelop
            %a{:href => "#"} email@infinityteam.com
            %br/
            %span.icon.icon-twitter
            %a{:href => "#"} @infinityteam.com
            %br/
            %span.icon.icon-facebook
            %a{:href => "#"} Infinity Agency
            %br/
        / col
        .col-md-8.fade-up
          %h3 Drop Us A Message
          %br/
          %br/
          #message
          %form#contactform{:action => "", :method => "post"}
            %input#name{:name => "name", :placeholder => "Name", :type => "text"}/
            %input#email{:name => "email", :placeholder => "Email", :type => "text"}/
            %input#website{:name => "website", :placeholder => "Website", :type => "text"}/
            %textarea#comments{:name => "comments", :placeholder => "Comments"}
            %input.btn.btn-outlined.btn-primary{:name => "submit", :type => "submit", :value => "Submit"}/
        / col
      / row
      .gap